<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Patch>
  <Operation Class="PatchOperationFindMod">
    <mods>
      <li>Combat Extended</li>
    </mods>
    <match Class="PatchOperationSequence">
      <success>Always</success>
      <operations>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="VG_IronWoodLog"]/tools/li[1]/label</xpath>
          <value>
            <label>손잡이</label>
          </value>
        </li>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="VG_IronWoodLog"]/tools/li[2]/label</xpath>
          <value>
            <label>머리</label>
          </value>
        </li>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="Bamboo"]/tools/li[1]/label</xpath>
          <value>
            <label>손잡이</label>
          </value>
        </li>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="Bamboo"]/tools/li[2]/label</xpath>
          <value>
            <label>머리</label>
          </value>
        </li>
      </operations>
    </match>
  </Operation>
  <Operation Class="PatchOperationFindMod">
    <mods>
      <li>SeedsPlease: Lite</li>
    </mods>
    <match Class="PatchOperationSequence">
      <success>Always</success>
      <operations>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="Seed_VG_Plant_TreeBamboo"]/label</xpath>
          <value>
            <label>대나무 씨앗</label>
          </value>
        </li>
      </operations>
    </match>
  </Operation>
  <Operation Class="PatchOperationReplace">
    <success>Always</success>
    <xpath>/Defs/TerrainDef[defName="FineIronwoodFloor"]/label</xpath>
    <value>
      <label>고급 철목 바닥</label>
    </value>
  </Operation>
  <Operation Class="PatchOperationReplace">
    <success>Always</success>
    <xpath>/Defs/TerrainDef[defName="FineIronwoodFloor"]/description</xpath>
    <value>
      <description>고급 철목 바닥재입니다. 이 훌륭한 바닥을 만들기 위해 많은 정성과 시간이 들어갑니다. 최고위 귀족에게 어울립니다.</description>
    </value>
  </Operation>
  <Operation Class="PatchOperationReplace">
    <success>Always</success>
    <xpath>/Defs/ResearchProjectDef[defName="Cocoa"]/description</xpath>
    <value>
      <description>맛좋은 초콜릿을 만들기 위한 코코아 나무를 재배할 수 있습니다. 초콜릿은 오락 욕구를 충족시키며, 가치있는 교역품이기도 합니다. \n\n나무와 덤불을 해금합니다.</description>
    </value>
  </Operation>
</Patch>